snippet.title: Five Nights at Freddy's: Help Wanted 2 Meta Quest Trailer
snippet.description: The wait is over! Five Nights at Freddy’s: Help Wanted 2 arrives on Meta Quest May 9th. Brace yourself for the horror—and the fun! Get ready for a heart-pounding VR experience. Pre-order your adventure now: https://bit.ly/HW2MQ
